title: DarkBasic Pro v6.9 - Inc. DarkSource - Activated
description:
Dark Basic Professional

Version 6.9 (March 2009)

Fully activated, no need for you to do anything.



On the disk is:

Dark Basic Professional v6.9 (Full version and Activated)
Dark Source (120 MB of code snippets)
DirectX 9.0c (Required)
Activator (this will reactivate DarkBasic Pro following an update)




I'm not one for blowing my own trumpet but this is better than if you paid for one. I have repackaged the whole thing using my own installer and is much more user friendly. I have altered it to work on Vista as well as XP. If you bought one, it would only work on XP.
